Job Description
- Web research, browsing multiple sites, scraping the internet for required data - Searching for appropriate web sources and contact persons for data capture - Data mining contact details: phone, addresses, emails of businesses and professionals - Collecting data into Excel Spreadsheets using copy paste and data entry functions - Email testing and validation, data formatting, deducing records and QA Checks - Meeting hourly and daily targets for research and data collection
Job Specification
Excellent proficiency with internet surfing, web navigation and data mining Ability to research, analyze and browse through various websites and make judgments Possess computer literacy, basic Excel and keyboarding skills including copy/paste, deducing, data formatting, file management and internet applications. Ability to read, write and comprehend English is a MUST.
Intermediate, B.Com graduates who are willing to learn and are career oriented.
Experience not required; however, preference will be given to applicants with prior BPO or internet research experience. Age limit: Min 19 & Max 24 years
